HEADWORD: Regrede
<hw>Re*grede"</hw> <pr>(r?*gr?d")</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>regredi</ets> to go back. Cf. <er>Regrade</er>,
<er>Regress</er>.]</ety> <def>To go back; to retrograde, as the apsis of
a planet's orbit.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Todhunter.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

